"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7422839\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 29, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pai1719680426187.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pai1719680426187.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pai1719680426187.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ecp1665702922959\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Combining Separate Entities\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ecp1665702922959__combining_separate_entities_140523\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Another way to improve performance is to combine several entities into a single entity.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ecp1665702922959__p_d45914e1_d45915e1_d45916e1\">For example, the original model has separate entities for ORDERLINE, COVERED_ITEM, DELIVERYLINE, and PART. You can combine these into a single entity called ASSEMBLY as shown in the following illustration:</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ecp1665702922959__fig_d45917e1_d45918e1_d45919e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Access Profile for Redefined Entity</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Access profile for redefined entity\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/accessprofileredefinedentity.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ecp1665702922959__p_d45923e1_d45924e1_d45925e1\">The access profile and the frames-within-frames diagram for this situation is shown in the following illustration:</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ecp1665702922959__fig_d45926e1_d45927e1_d45928e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Access Profile and Frame-Within-Frames Using Redefined Entity</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Access profile and frame-within-frames using redefined entity\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/accessprofilefwfredefinedentity.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ecp1665702922959__p_d45932e1_d45933e1_d45934e1\">The amended access profile is shown in the following table.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Access Profile Statistics for Redefined Entity</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__1\">\n Access profile\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__2\">\n Via\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__3\">\n Selected Occurrences (avg.)\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__4\">\n Access Stress Value\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__1\">\n &gt;Configuration\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__2\">\n configuration_id\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__3\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__4\">\n 1\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__1\">\n Configuration&gt;&gt;Assembly\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__2\">\n configuration_id\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__3\">\n 5\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__4\">\n 5\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__1\">\n Assembly&gt;Material\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__2\">\n material_id\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__3\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__4\">\n 5\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__1 ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__2 ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__3\">\n                     Total Access Stress Rating\n                  </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ecp1665702922959__table_d4391e1_d4392e1_d4393e1__entry__4\">\n 11\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422839\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422839\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-do